ul.li:
fetches a GDK-Proton built from a WineGDK fork that implements XUser
          and request signing, so you sign in to Microsoft inside the game —
          no relay, no proxy;

fixes a crash on the first launch after install, caused by
              Proton's OpenXR runtime — VR is now fully disabled so the game
              starts straight into normal (flat) mode;

initialises the Wine prefix before installing the input and
              login components, fixing a "system32 not found" failure on a
              fresh install;
